{"tid":1798743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紅磡站出軌事故　機電署初步排除由外物或惡意破壞所致","createTime":"2019-12-26T12:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T04:51:09.000Z","uid":258649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"74d1ff0df58621fd759dae3e86fdfd1cfd73558b","tid":1798743,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】九月中港鐵紅磡站東鐵綫列車出軌事故，機電工程署初步<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">排除是由外物或惡意破壞所致</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n今年九月中，一列東鐵綫列車駛進紅磡站時有三卡車出軌。機電署回覆查詢指，初步排除事故是由外物或惡意破壞所致，調查仍進行中，署方已聘請本地及海外專家協助，預計於明年2月底前完成。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=374636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374636&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=95b59be6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374636&h=75365955\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=374636</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇人知今時今日仲搭党鐵既人咩心態,一年出軌3次,刺激過坐過山車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZO2i2Si.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZO2i2Si.jpg&h=01897540&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b1fd04e6ec3a3493e0855585d474bd4b1b4a0a4","tid":1798743,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:31:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4de68074fb61f6408785a2aa30a0f6cd0eb919d","tid":1798743,"uid":31863,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:37:09.000Z","msg":"屌你又話有爆徙切斷路軌"},{"pid":"c9bad1372708f26e4822e5db4f34819cb6bb46b6","tid":1798743,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:40:27.000Z","msg":"自己問題走去賴人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af